          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The areas of all gamma peaks observed were corrected",
                "for efficiency of detection and the activities of the",
                "radioactive products were calculated separately for",
                "each peak on the basis of the nuclear data.",
                "No correction were made either for the energy spread at",
                "each foil, as resulting from foil thickness variations,",
                "or for energy losses at the preceding foils.  The",
                "eventual losses of reaction products by recoil were",
                "assumed to be negligible."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-T",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " An estimation of the average error of the",
                "excitation functions is given in table.  This average",
                "error includes:"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-S",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Statistical error",
                "  * the uncertainties due to the target foil thickness,",
                "  * the beam current,",
                "  * the detector efficiency and",
                "  * the analysis of the gamma spectra.",
                "The uncertainty due to the analysis of the gamma",
                "spectra differ from case to case.  Much greater",
                "uncertainties were taken into account in those cases",
                "where complex peak evaluation and subtraction of",
                "activities could not be avoided during the calculation",
                "of the cross sections.",
                "In many of these cases only a rough lower limit",
                "estimation of the error could be given."
              ]
            }
          ],
